            <h5><b>Portraiture</b></h5>
            <p>A portrait is typically defined as a representation of a specific individual, such as the artist might meet in life. A portrait does not merely record someone’s features, however, but says something about who he or she is, offering a vivid sense of a real person’s presence. <a href="https://www.metmuseum.org/toah/hd/port/hd_port.htm" target="blank">Read more here.</a></p>
