            <h5><b>Concept Art</b></h5>
            <p>The main goal of concept art is to convey a visual representation of a design, idea, and/or mood for use in films, video games, animation, or comic books before it is put into the final product. <a href="https://www.creativebloq.com/career/what-concept-art-11121155" target="blank">Read more here.</a></p>
