            <h5><b>WPAP</b></h5>
            <p>WPAP (Wedha Pop Art Portrait) is human portrait illustration style (usually famous figures) dominated flat fields bloom color is placed in the front, middle, and back to cause dimension. <a href="https://hubpages.com/art/wedha-pop-art-portrait-wpap" target="blank">Read more here.</a></p>
